data.title: High Tide + Cove B Site Execute + Safe Plant Combo
data.description: Use your High Tide to execute onto Site with your team, and then use your Cove to make it somewhat safe for you to plant the Spike.

data.title: High Tide + Cove A Site Full Execute
data.description: Use this High Tide + Cove Combo to execute onto A Site with your team, or fake an A push.
